              30-3-35(5)(b)(i): in odd-numbered years:
                  30-3-35(5)(b)(i)(A): the noncustodial parent shall provide notice to the custodial parent by May 1; and
                  30-3-35(5)(b)(i)(B): the custodial parent shall provide notice to the noncustodial parent by May 15; and
              30-3-35(5)(b)(ii): in even-numbered years:
